project_descr: The project  will consist of the construction of a 1.8 kilometer roadway from the New Jericho Wholesale Market to the proposed Jericho Agro Industrial Park.

outputs.output_descr: the goal of the project is to build approximately 1.8 kilometers of roadway between the newly built Jericho Whole-sale Market and the proposed Jericho Agro-Industrial Zone; in order to enhance access for future Agro-industrial park.

project_title: rehabilitation of the agro industrial park road
